      "content": "it felt so specific though. like a physical pulse in my head. i didnt even look at my phone until i felt that ringing. if i'm actually picking up on these high-frequency patterns subconsciously, it would explain why i always seem to get these weird physical symptoms right before a big move. do you think it's possible for someone to actually be wired to sense these kinds of massive data shifts intuitively?",
